#: ../../../compiling-a-contract.rst:485
msgid "Errors"
msgstr "錯誤"

#: ../../../compiling-a-contract.rst:487
msgid ""
"Each error includes a ``component`` field, indicating the stage at which it "
"occurred:"
msgstr "每個錯誤都包含一個 ``component`` 欄位，指示錯誤發生的階段："

#: ../../../compiling-a-contract.rst:489
msgid ""
"``json``: Errors that occur while parsing the input JSON. Usually, a result "
"of invalid JSON or a required value that is missing."
msgstr ""
"``json``：解析輸入 JSON 時發生的錯誤。通常是無效的 JSON 或缺少必要值的結果。"

#: ../../../compiling-a-contract.rst:490
msgid ""
"``parser``: Errors that occur while parsing the contracts. Usually, a result "
"of invalid Vyper syntax."
msgstr "``parser``：解析合約時發生的錯誤。通常是無效的 Vyper 語法的結果。"

#: ../../../compiling-a-contract.rst:491
msgid "``compiler``: Errors that occur while compiling the contracts."
msgstr "``compiler``：編譯合約時發生的錯誤。"

#: ../../../compiling-a-contract.rst:492
msgid ""
"``vyper``: Unexpected errors that occur within Vyper. If you receive an "
"error of this type, please open an issue."
msgstr ""
"``vyper``：Vyper 內部發生的意外錯誤。如果您收到此類型的錯誤，請開啟一個 "
"Issue。"

#: ../../../compiling-a-contract.rst:494
msgid ""
"You can also use the ``--traceback`` flag to receive a standard Python "
"traceback when an error is encountered."
msgstr ""
"您也可以使用 ``--traceback`` 旗標，在遇到錯誤時接收標準的 Python traceback。"
